     A*** ALDPW3S  *****************************************
     A* SCAN IN CASE LABEL                                 *
     A*     LEC.          2021.10.13                       *
     A******************************************************
     A                                      DSPSIZ(24 80 *DS3)
     A                                      CHGINPDFT
     A                                      PRINT
     A          R DSP01
     A                                      CF03(03)
